{"tid":1265703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉康宣佈成立香港效益主義黨","createTime":"2019-06-29T10:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T10:30:29.000Z","uid":18245,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c77dd9bdeb62eca49c29185d7deee70adcc904f7","tid":1265703,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T10:17:48.000Z","msg":"「學生動源」前成員、<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">17歲的劉康</span></strong>今日（29日）宣布成立「香港效益主義黨」。劉康手持John Stuart Mill的《Utilitarianism》，表明成立政黨旨在宣揚效益主義，並<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">爭取香港獨立，因香港獨立才符合效益主義原則，能夠保障香港人的自由和文化。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n早前主張港獨的香港民族黨被取締，劉康稱港府根本沒有認受性，所以不怕港府取締，現未計劃何時開戶口。他稱建黨沒有金主，但不便透露資金來源，不會公開黨員身分及人數，亦不透露未來有何活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190629/s00001/1561795630819/%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%8B%95%E6%BA%90%E5%89%8D%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9%E9%BB%A8%E3%80%8D-%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E7%88%AD%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E4%BF%9D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190629%2Fs00001%2F1561795630819%2F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25BA%2590%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2595%2588%25E7%259B%258A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E3%2580%258D-%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2598%258E%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E4%25BF%259D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmqwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=30983df9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190629%2Fs00001%2F1561795630819%2F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25